original_title: Brooklyn: Village Rd. E. - Neck Rd.
text:
(1)
76 Village Road East, west side, between Neck Road and West 1st Street, showing the Schumacher house occupied by a Van Sicklen in 1860, and a Mrs. Van Sicklen in 1873.
April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, a more extensive view west to West 1st Street.
March 2, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
